+- `$tries = 3`
+- Construtor: `ConsentSubject $subject`, `string $channel`, `string $rawToken`
+- URL: `route('privacy.revoke', ['token' => $rawToken])`
+- View: `resources/views/emails/revocation-link.blade.php`
